Custom vim settings and plugins

Install:
    -- Link repo to filesystem --
    ln -s vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s . ~/.vim

    -- Install Vundle --
    git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim

    -- Install all plugins --
    :PluginInstall (inside of vim)

Requires:
    - vim compiled with python 2
    - git is installed
    - (optional) silversearcher-ag for speady ctrlp
    - (optional ctags for easytag generation
      sudo apt-get install exuberant-ctags
      or
      http://ctags.sourceforge.net/
